summary: Adds a row boat near to Windstad manor and Solitude docks to travel between the two locations.
descriptionHtml:
This is a quick and simple mod that adds row boats to Windstad Manor and Solitude docks.  Walk up to a boat and activate it to be transported to the other.  A short amount of in-game time will pass when using the boats.

Windstad Boat - Slightly North of the fish hatchery.
Solitude Boat - South West end of the dock.
(See pictures tab for more detail).

This mod does [b][u]not[/u][/b] require Hearthfire.

*Made as a request for 'reindeer 51'*
author: Thicketford
